data.description: Come live in the quiet country near a state park!  This charming classic ranch home exudes character and warmth. Step inside to discover pristine hardwood floors spanning the entirety of this inviting space. The living room seamlessly connects to a formal dining area and kitchen, creating an ideal setting for gatherings and entertaining. The open kitchen adds a touch of modern convenience while maintaining the home's inviting atmosphere.  There's also a versatile bonus room ready to adapt to your needs. The expansive laundry room off the main bath offers ample storage, ensuring clutter is never an issue. Outside, your oasis awaits. Lounge by the above-ground pool on lazy afternoons, tend to your favorite plants in the greenhouse, or explore the diverse array of flowers that bloom throughout the property. With plenty of room for a garden, your green thumb will flourish here. Plus, a barn with shed roofs provides additional storage space for all your outdoor essentials.  Conveniently located less than 2 miles from Hard Labor Creek State Park, endless outdoor adventures are right at your doorstep and only minutes away.  For added peace of mind, the seller is also offering a 1-year home warranty.  Nestled in the highly desired Morgan County, this gem won't stay on the market for long. Don't miss your chance to make this beautiful property your forever home.
